# 🛒 Product Backlog – Online Store (Variety Shop)

## 🎯 Epic 1: First Impression & Trust
**Goal:** Users quickly understand and trust the store

- **US01**: As a user, I want to clearly see what the store sells when I enter, so I can decide if I am interested.
- **US02**: As a user, I want to see a clear value proposition, so I understand what makes the store different.
- **US03**: As a user, I want to see trust signals (reviews, social media, contact info), so I feel safe buying.

**Priority:** High

---

## 🗂️ Epic 2: Catalog & Navigation
**Goal:** Help users find products easily

- **US04**: As a user, I want to see clear categories, so I can browse easily.
- **US05**: As a user, I want to use filters (price, size, color), so I can quickly find what I need.
- **US06**: As a user, I want a functional search bar, so I can find specific products.

**Priority:** High

---

## 📸 Epic 3: Product Visualization
**Goal:** Build trust through visuals

- **US07**: As a user, I want to see high-quality images, so I can evaluate the product.
- **US08**: As a user, I want to see multiple angles of the product, so I can understand it better.
- **US09**: As a user, I want to see real-life or in-use photos, so I can trust the purchase.

**Priority:** High

---

## 📝 Epic 4: Product Information
**Goal:** Reduce doubts before purchase

- **US10**: As a user, I want to see complete product descriptions (material, size, etc.), so I can make informed decisions.
- **US11**: As a user, I want to know what is included in the product, so I avoid confusion.

**Priority:** High

---

## 💸 Epic 5: Pricing & Transparency
**Goal:** Avoid surprises

- **US12**: As a user, I want to see the full price upfront, so I avoid hidden costs.
- **US13**: As a user, I want to see clear promotions, so I can take advantage of offers.

**Priority:** High

---

## 🚚 Epic 6: Shipping
**Goal:** Provide clear delivery information

- **US14**: As a user, I want to know the shipping cost before checkout, so I can decide whether to continue.
- **US15**: As a user, I want to know the estimated delivery time, so I can plan my purchase.

**Priority:** High

---

## 💳 Epic 7: Payments
**Goal:** Make purchasing easy

- **US16**: As a user, I want multiple payment methods, so I can choose the most convenient one.
- **US17**: As a user, I want a simple checkout process, so I can complete my purchase easily.

**Priority:** High

---

## ⭐ Epic 8: Reviews & Social Proof
**Goal:** Build trust through other users

- **US18**: As a user, I want to see customer reviews, so I can trust the product.
- **US19**: As a user, I want to see customer photos, so I can validate quality.

**Priority:** Medium-High

---

## 📱 Epic 9: Design & Performance
**Goal:** Smooth experience (especially mobile)

- **US20**: As a user, I want the store to work well on my phone, so I can shop easily.
- **US21**: As a user, I want fast loading times, so I don’t waste time.

**Priority:** High

---

## 🤝 Epic 10: Support & Trust
**Goal:** Ensure customer support

- **US22**: As a user, I want to see clear policies (returns, exchanges), so I feel secure.
- **US23**: As a user, I want fast contact options (chat/social media), so I can resolve doubts quickly.

**Priority:** High

---

## 🎁 Epic 11: Customer Retention (Bonus)
**Goal:** Encourage repeat purchases

- **US24**: As a user, I want to receive promotions, so I get better deals.
- **US25**: As a user, I want a nice delivery experience (packaging/details), so I feel valued.

**Priority:** Low-Medium

---

# 📊 Prioritization (MVP)

## MUST HAVE
- US01 – US17  
- US20 – US23  

## SHOULD HAVE
- US18 – US19  

## NICE TO HAVE
- US24 – US25  

---

# 💡 Notes
Focus on delivering a simple, trustworthy, and fast experience first.  
Core features like catalog, product pages, checkout, and shipping clarity are critical for conversion.
